        "1 mg Adrenalin ampulünü 10 mL saline sulandırın (1:10.000). Bu çözeltiden 0.1 mL/kg uygulayın." to "Dilute 1 mg Epinephrine ampoule with 10 mL saline (1:10,000). Administer 0.1 mL/kg of this solution.",
