        "Bakteri hücre duvarı sentezini inhibe eder, cerrahi profilaksinin temel ilacıdır." to "It inhibits bacterial cell wall synthesis and is the main drug of surgical prophylaxis.",
        "Bakteri hücre duvarı sentezini inhibe eder." to "It inhibits bacterial cell wall synthesis.",
        "Bakteri hücresine girdikten sonra aktif ara metabolitlerine indirgenir, bu metabolitler bakteri DNA yapısını bozarak sentezini engeller." to "After entering the bacterial cell, it is reduced to its active intermediate metabolites, which disrupt the bacterial DNA structure and prevent its synthesis.",
        "Bakteriyel 30S ribozomal alt birimine bağlanarak mRNA kod okunmasını bozar, bakteri protein sentezini irreversibl inhibe eder." to "It disrupts mRNA code reading by binding to the bacterial 30S ribosomal subunit and irreversibly inhibits bacterial protein synthesis.",
        "Bakteriyel 50S ribozomal alt birimine geri dönüşümlü bağlanarak protein sentezini (peptid zincir uzamasını) inhibe eder." to "It inhibits protein synthesis (peptide chain elongation) by reversibly binding to the bacterial 50S ribosomal subunit.",
        "Bakteriyel hücre duvarı peptidoglikan sentezini D-alanyl-D-alanine bölgesine bağlanarak inhibe eder, hücre ölümünü sağlar." to "It inhibits bacterial cell wall peptidoglycan synthesis by binding to the D-alanyl-D-alanine region, causing cell death.",
        "Balon ile manuel ventilasyon yaparken havayolu direnci nasıl? Göğüs kalkıyor mu?" to "What is the airway resistance during bag-mask ventilation? Is the chest rising?",
