        "Cancer (eg, breast cancer): The clinical significance of hyperprolactinemia in patients with breast cancer or other prolactin-dependent tumors is unknown...." to "Cancer (eg, breast cancer): The clinical significance of hyperprolactinemia in patients with breast cancer or other prolactin-dependent tumors is unknown....",
        "Cannot Intubate Cannot Oxygenate (CICO) durumu ilan edildi! Acil neşter-bougie krikotirotomi algoritmasını göster." to "Cannot Intubate Cannot Oxygenate (CICO) status declared! Demonstrate the emergency scalpel-bougie cricothyrotomy algorithm.",
