        "Cardiac effects: May precipitate or aggravate angina pectoris or induce cardiac arrhythmias; use with caution especially in patients with cardiac disease or those receiving drugs t..." to "Cardiac effects: May precipitate or aggravate angina pectoris or induce cardiac arrhythmias; use with caution especially in patients with cardiac disease or those receiving drugs t...",
        "Cardiovascular disease: Use is contraindicated in patients with coronary artery disease (CAD). Use with caution in patients with cerebral vascular accidents and suspected CAD; myoc..." to "Cardiovascular disease: Use is contraindicated in patients with coronary artery disease (CAD). Use with caution in patients with cerebral vascular accidents and suspected CAD; myoc...",
        "Cardiovascular disease: Use with caution in patients with cardiovascular disease (arrhythmia, coronary insufficiency, hypertension, heart failure). In a scientific statement from t..." to "Cardiovascular disease: Use with caution in patients with cardiovascular disease (arrhythmia, coronary insufficiency, hypertension, heart failure). In a scientific statement from t...",
        "Cardiovascular disease: Use with caution in patients with cardiovascular disease. Other warnings/precautions:..." to "Cardiovascular disease: Use with caution in patients with cardiovascular disease. Other warnings/precautions:...",
