        "Floppy iris syndrome: Intraoperative floppy iris syndrome has been observed in cataract surgery patients who were treated with alpha 1 -blockers. There appears to be no benefit in ..." to "Floppy iris syndrome: Intraoperative floppy iris syndrome has been observed in cataract surgery patients who were treated with alpha 1 -blockers. There appears to be no benefit in ...",
