        "Hypotension: [US Boxed Warning]: Excessive hypotension resulting in compromised perfusion of vital organs may occur; continuous blood pressure monitoring by experienced personnel i..." to "Hypotension: [US Boxed Warning]: Excessive hypotension resulting in compromised perfusion of vital organs may occur; continuous blood pressure monitoring by experienced personnel i...",
        "Hypovolemia: Address hypovolemia before initiating therapy; patients who are hypotensive from hypovolemia may experience severe peripheral and visceral vasoconstriction, decreased ..." to "Hypovolemia: Address hypovolemia before initiating therapy; patients who are hypotensive from hypovolemia may experience severe peripheral and visceral vasoconstriction, decreased ...",
        "Hücre dışı kalsiyum konsantrasyonunu artırarak miyokard uyarılabilirliğini, iletimini ve kontraktilitesini düzenler. Magnezyum ve potasyumun kardiyak toksik etkilerini antagonize eder." to "It regulates myocardial excitability, conduction and contractility by increasing extracellular calcium concentration. It antagonizes the cardiac toxic effects of magnesium and potassium.",
        "Hücre dışı sıvıdaki bikarbonat iyonu konsantrasyonunu artırarak hidrojen iyonlarını nötralize eder ve kan pH'ını yükseltir." to "It neutralizes hydrogen ions and increases blood pH by increasing the bicarbonate ion concentration in the extracellular fluid.",
        "Hücre içinde lizozomal enzimlerle aminoasitlere yıkılır" to "It is broken down into amino acids by lysosomal enzymes within the cell.",
