        "Nonsteroid antiinflamatuvar (NSAİİ) analjezik; hafif-orta ağrı tedavisinde kullanılır (PDF özet formatında detaylı uyarı bulunmuyor)." to "Nonsteroidal anti-inflammatory (NSAID) analgesic; used for treatment of mild to moderate pain (concise PDF format, no detailed warnings provided).",
        "Nonsteroidal anti-inflammatory drug–induced gastric ulcers, prevention: Refer to adult dosing. Adverse Reactions The following adverse drug reactions and incidences are derived from product labeling unless otherwise specified. Adverse reactions reported in adults. &gt;10%: Gastrointestinal: Abdominal pain, diarrhea (including severe diarrhea) 1% to 10%: Gastrointestinal: Constipation, dyspepsia, f..." to "Nonsteroidal anti-inflammatory drug–induced gastric ulcers, prevention: Refer to adult dosing. Adverse Reactions The following adverse drug reactions and incidences are derived from product labeling unless otherwise specified. Adverse reactions reported in adults. &gt;10%: Gastrointestinal: Abdominal pain, diarrhea (including severe diarrhea) 1% to 10%: Gastrointestinal: Constipation, dyspepsia, f...",
