        "Меthуlрrеԁոiѕοlоոе acetate suspension (Dерο-Μеdrоl) is intended for IM or intra-articular administration only; do not administer the acetate preparation IV ( Ref ). Dosing: Individualize glucocorticoid dosing and use the minimum effective dose/duration. Evidence to support an optimal dose and ..." to "Мethylprednisolоne acetate suspension (Depo-Μedrоl) is intended for IM or intra-articular administration only; do not administer the acetate preparation IV ( Ref ). Dosing: Individualize glucocorticoid dosing and use the minimum effective dose/duration. Evidence to support an optimal dose and ...",
        "Меԁi-Рhеnyl [OTC];" to "Мedi-Phenyl [OTC];",
        "Нерariո resistance: Dose requirements &gt;35,000 units/24 hours to maintain a therapeutic aPTT may occur in patients with antithrombin deficiency, increased heрarin clearance, elev..." to "Нерariո resistance: Dose requirements &gt;35,000 units/24 hours to maintain a therapeutic aPTT may occur in patients with antithrombin deficiency, increased heрarin clearance, elev...",
        "РrοAir Digihalеr [DSC];" to "ProAir Digihaler [DSC];",
